23)Write a code that displays the sum of all the even numbers from the given list.
```
numbers = [12, 75, 150, 180, 145, 525, 50]
```

numbers = [12, 75, 150, 180, 145, 525, 50]
total=0
for i in numbers:
  if(i%2==0):
    total=total+i
print("The sum of numbers is" ,total)

