Q85. Write a Python program to find cumulative sum of a list.

lst1 = [1,2,3,67,93,74,64,7,10]
lst_cuml = []
sum = 0
for i in range(0,len(lst1)):
	sum = sum + lst1[i]
	lst_cuml.append(sum)
print(lst_cuml)   
